Look at our bookshelves and find something new to read. This app is a large catalog of audiobooks which you can listen to right from your device.
Dive deep into the world of fairytales, discover classical works, absorb the atmosphere of horror, listen to the Brothers Grimm’s fairy tales in German! And now you can even read the subtitles for the book you are listening to due to the power of Artificial Intelligence!


Check out the works of famous writers such as Bierce, Chekhov, Van Dyke, and many others:

- Subtitles for the book you are listening to
- 72 audiobooks in different genres;
- 7 categories from adventure to horror;
- a new book every week;
- listening to the books online;
- possibility to listen offline anytime.

Audio Books & Ebooks Reader - your personal audio collection of short stories, written by world-famous authors.


Privacy Policy: http://musictopia.club/privacy
Terms Of Use: https://musictopia.club/tos

MoNovel es una plataforma de lectura profesional para novelas originales. Hay más de 10,000 maravillosas novelas originales, puede leer más historias sobre romance, fantasía, amor, suspenso y terror, etc. creadas por muchos autores excelentes. Puede disfrutar del placer de leer en cualquier momento y en cualquier lugar.

Actualización diaria: todos los días se publican nuevas historias;

Lectura fácil: puede personalizar una variedad de modos de lectura;

MoNovel está llena de historias que te encantan leer.
